name: Cosmo-Specian General
effect:
This card is treated as a Normal Monster while in the hand.
(1) When this card is sent to the Graveyard to activate a DARK Spellcaster-type monster's effect: Add 1 "Cosmo-Specian" card from your Deck to your hand.
(2) While this card is in your GY: You can banish this card; Special Summon as many Level 1 "Cosmo-Specian" monsters with different names as possible from your hand.
